 D3_USSR_Execution {
  m_sTitle "III. Execution"
  m_sTextData "a. Commander's Intent"\
  ""\
  "The purpose of this operation is to break through the enemy screen."\
  "The end state is that either Sinystov or Vavilovo has been mostly secured, and the company has reconsolidated further south west."\
  ""\
  "b. Concept of Operations"\
  ""\
  "Phase I: Assault and gain control of either Sinystov or Vavilovo."\
  "Phase II: All units proceed further south west, and the company consolidates near the pine forest."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "USSR"
  }
