 D3_US_Execution {
  m_sTitle "III. Execution"
  m_sTextData "a. Commander's Intent"\
  ""\
  "The platoon is to prevent the enemy reconnaissance company from seizing either Sinystok or Vavilovo, which it will likely attempt in an effort to break through to the south west, and locate our main force."\
  ""\
  "b. Concept of Operations"\
  ""\
  "Phase I: The infantry prepares to defend both towns, while the LAR platoon screens ahead to identify the enemy axis of advance."\
  "Phase II: When the enemies objective becomes clear, the Rifle platoons reserve squad reallocates its forces as required, and the platoon leader requests reinforcements from the sister platoon."\
  ""\
  "c. Scheme of Fires"\
  ""\
  "A mortar squad from weapons platoon (4'2) is on-call for fire support, it is to prepare firing solutions for identified TRPs in advance."\
  "Firing solutions for the 3 marked TRPs have already calculated."
